      <h2 class="heading pad-bottom-15">
        <span class="small-heading">About Direct Derivatives</span>
        <span class="big-heading">Who we are</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="lead">
        Direct Derivatives has a unique team culture with all professionals working together across different countries and time zones to provide seamless and round the clock execution services to investors worldwide. With offices in Australia, United Kingdom, Seoul, Shenzhen and USA, Our 49 professionals, around half of whom are senior professionals, have an average of almost 20 years of relevant experience. Our senior partners have an excess of 40 years industry experience providing the knowledge to operate successfully.
      </p>
      <p>
        Direct Derivatives partners first established in the futures markers in 2001, later transforming the company in 2006 into a Global Forex brokerage firm headquartered in Australia, Direct FX Trading Pty Ltd, becoming a leading independent forex broker among with one the largest trading volumes in the world. The strength of our Australasian business has enabled us to grow rapidly in the East and create an integrated global service for clients, with technology and support base in Europe and the Americas.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our clients include Brokerage companies around the world, retail forex traders, commodities traders, asset managers, banks, CTAs, and hedge funds. Direct Derivatives also provide exchanges with Market Making services in Currency and Metals Futures and Options.
